{"tid":1521792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"應對顏料水","createTime":"2019-08-31T10:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:20.000Z","uid":207197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"521acd859d29f53a1f3c5931da8c0101af86238e","tid":1521792,"uid":207197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:49:57.000Z","msg":"應對 #顏料水<br />\n<br />\n特性<br />\n染料入面有稀釋左嘅 聚甲基丙烯酸甲酯 Acrylici 成份，乾左之後會好難洗甩，就咁揾水無用，一定要盡快清洗<br />\n<br />\n建議<br />\n包全身，完事棄裝<br />\n- 頭：先用衫 #包頭 、頭盔、眼罩、口罩 <br />\n- 頸、手：保鮮紙<br />\n- 身：全可即棄black bloc<br />\n- 鞋：即棄鞋、拎多對<br />\n- 重要：最上層要着件防水外套／雨褸<br />\n<br />\n皮膚<br />\n方法一：醋 + 水 (比例1:3)<br />\n將手浸喺醋水約5分鐘，要邊浸邊捽<br />\n<br />\n方法二：蘇打粉 + 溫水 (比例1:1)<br />\n蘇打粉水要攪勻，最好係用流動溫水邊沖邊捽，來回倒五六次就得<br />\n<br />\n如果有兄弟身上面中左好多染色劑，要揾個浴缸浸落去！<br />\n<br />\n衣物<br />\n方法一：氨水（即係阿摩尼亞水）<br />\n用氨水浸15分鐘，然後再用冷水浸15分鐘<br />\n<br />\n方法二：棄掉染色衣物"},{"pid":"83486656a91be789e506dc8f4fba01b2de4d8e72","tid":1521792,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:50:43.000Z","msg":"［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal"},{"pid":"6356149ca9c6455bc4ba683216656a7d107ceb2e","tid":1521792,"uid":207197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:50:50.000Z","msg":"接放學嘅人可以準備下"},{"pid":"3b108f3d1c1b8380a9d01ffc90a48edd19e8628a","tid":1521792,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:51:02.000Z","msg":"1845 現場手足報料：「啱啱試過含酒精濕紙巾可抹走顏色水」<br />\n幫忙廣傳"},{"pid":"573a21807aa5fe98de4ed5bb2aea4227e3e70823","tid":1521792,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:51:27.000Z","msg":"地區的兒子需要接送<br />\n<br />\n要拖鞋換 小心螢光鞋底路"},{"pid":"8a04cbd1a6faba1b6d14b42c5b6569789bdf11a3","tid":1521792,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1c6f83ba8c696ca60e1b3fc5ce02e48b609a8b","tid":1521792,"uid":314979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xAhmXsv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxAhmXsv.gif&h=398db0bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b48ea63626df6cf35b1b2255f18af710faaeaf0","tid":1521792,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:20.000Z","msg":"就杜浩成法官作出有罪假定及煽動他人侵權之言論作出投訴（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1521682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1521682</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}